description=Auto-sorts downloads into categorized folders. NEW in v4.3.1: Magisk module detection. NEW in v4.3: Recursive scanning, auto-exclusion of base_path, custom folder exclusions. Edit config.json to customize. Works with Magisk and KernelSU.
